rows.label: qst630503_msg0001
rows.name: Gwahahaha! That got my Ether pumping!

rows.label: qst630503_msg0002
rows.name: I'm all tuckered out now...

rows.label: qst630503_msg0003
rows.name: Ten'i, how are you feeling?

rows.label: qst630503_msg0004
rows.name: Normal.

rows.label: qst630503_msg0005
rows.name: But...

rows.label: qst630503_msg0006
rows.name: It isn't over yet.

rows.label: qst630503_msg0007
rows.name:
Well now! Things are
getting interesting!

rows.label: qst630503_msg0008
rows.name:
Dealing with one was hard enough,
and now there's three...?

rows.label: qst630503_msg0009
rows.name: We will be fine...

rows.label: qst630503_msg0010
rows.name: If I just release my power...

rows.label: qst630503_msg0011
rows.name: Grhh... My...power...!

rows.label: qst630503_msg0012
rows.name: Ten'i, no! You can't!

rows.label: qst630503_msg0013
rows.name: ...My power...dissipated?

rows.label: qst630503_msg0014
rows.name: Raiko, was it you...?

rows.label: qst630503_msg0015
rows.name:
I just, uh, suddenly thought I'd
better... do something, I guess...

rows.label: qst630503_msg0016
rows.name:
With you controlling the output,
the fight would be much easier.

rows.label: qst630503_msg0017
rows.name: Now there's an idea!

rows.label: qst630503_msg0018
rows.name:
Hey, Driver, can me and
Ten'i go after one of 'em?

rows.label: qst630503_msg0019
rows.name:
It's all right - we can get some
extra pairs of hands to help!
So just you leave it to us!

rows.label: qst630503_msg0020
rows.name:
If Raiko and Ten'i can go after
one... It'd make me look bad not
to call dibs on one too, right?!

rows.label: qst630503_msg0021
rows.name:
If we handle the other two,
I imagine you can manage
one without us, right?

rows.label: qst630503_msg0022
rows.name:
Or we can just take all three
on at once and pound 'em flat.
That's definitely an option!

rows.label: qst630503_msg0023
rows.name:
Hell, I think that's pretty damn exciting!
But you're the Driver here, so what's it
gonna be? Merc-style, or all-out brawl?

rows.label: qst630503_msg0024
rows.name:
Maybe we should head back to Rigitte
Harbor and think it through...

rows.label: qst630503_msg0101
rows.name: Are you all right?
